{"tid":1138531,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[日/台版] 天華百劍斬 -21- 徘徊在似歐又霉之間 望不穿這限池深坑 歐過總要還 無謂多貪","createTime":"2019-05-04T14:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T15:05:09.000Z","uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5c41ad3344cc09f66403223d493eca6752663a","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/192457_21d3552879585f469123ae213309a457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F192457_21d3552879585f469123ae213309a457.jpg&h=fe048ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/174247_f5c41ba06ea71349c17b24d5c28da3fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F174247_f5c41ba06ea71349c17b24d5c28da3fb.jpg&h=46b56671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共鬥已經實裝 可以連機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qxggny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qxggny.png&h=64a48868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻game個個月都送新衫 新衫會有新配音同劇情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLJDHhS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLJDHhS.jpg&h=42ebeb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Va_jKQKw4p0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVa_jKQKw4p0&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=0a84ebee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Va_jKQKw4p0</a><br />\n5月活動繼續會有衫送以及CV會唱event專屬bgm<br />\n<br />\nAndroid下載 : <a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4036&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=797a1bad\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4036</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS下載 : <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id989719261?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid989719261%3Fl%3Dja%26ls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b47640d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id989719261?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n以上係日版link 台版去apps store下載<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhQ9Bk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhQ9Bk8.jpg&h=c0ed95a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橫向動作遊戲 人設同SD好高質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/210252_8f5dc8c7a9683bca7840eafebff360a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F210252_8f5dc8c7a9683bca7840eafebff360a3.jpg&h=13b2d949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POsFof2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOsFof2.jpg&h=4d1c48a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/160738_4591c434628a285bff7f057b3439b7eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F160738_4591c434628a285bff7f057b3439b7eb.png&h=89eab6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNZAb9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNZAb9s.jpg&h=848b195f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n破衣系統 最期待的畫面出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/193657_0bc3a29c158cc23026826d3ff14bde25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F193657_0bc3a29c158cc23026826d3ff14bde25.gif&h=5264b020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所有主線/活動/角色故事都有全語音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/06Pa22J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F06Pa22J.gif&h=d3e61038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觸摸角色隨住親密度變化會有唔同表情同說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rVfMFad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrVfMFad.gif&h=c8ac7b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新增體感mode 上下左右隨你鐘意點搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共鬥Gameplay<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U8Q5J2oLVLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU8Q5J2oLVLY&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=82c0c7a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U8Q5J2oLVLY</a></div>"},{"pid":"978fac822a3ec3aa5f78e9555e216d1a0475e5c0","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">本月焦點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWPZDAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWPZDAU.jpg&h=4bf10ee4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n5月活動新角及衣裝情報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTocd87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTocd87.jpg&h=a0233d5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HevaLfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHevaLfO.jpg&h=35ed96ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2dLy88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2dLy88.jpg&h=781f702c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nJK三人組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTWRhSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTWRhSi.jpg&h=6d3e3cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUspCSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUspCSi.jpg&h=1565aa89&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFt8j5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFt8j5K.jpg&h=6f9e69e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6bJTqN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6bJTqN.jpg&h=629d6345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8Sw2i9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8Sw2i9.jpg&h=62c0c248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxH5njk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoxH5njk.jpg&h=8bb085aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NRWmNd3xOb0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNRWmNd3xOb0&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9fab69c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NRWmNd3xOb0</a><br />\n新登場巫劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60SgFQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60SgFQ6.jpg&h=86f6259a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2周年公佈將會制作短篇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"68b23fdefd179bb655d9bffe89d11340eb3886e6","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首抽建議</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n以下都係限定 日版要月尾先有得抽 台服就月頭<br />\n入坑前最好喺post問一問 因為每月新限角都唔同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>七星劍</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QmdAiiuqR94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQmdAiiuqR94&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=deeaa205\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QmdAiiuqR94</a><br />\n最新限定 清怪快 全地圖奧義<br />\n<br />\n<ins>丙子椒林劍</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jChuj4ETw7A?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjChuj4ETw7A%3Flist%3DPLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7811cba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jChuj4ETw7A?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8</a><br />\n可以chok招 手動清怪輸出最強<br />\n<br />\n<ins>三日月宗近</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uE1TTagPedk?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuE1TTagPedk%3Flist%3DPLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=1fd4deeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uE1TTagPedk?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8</a><br />\n萬能型 不適合auto<br />\n<br />\n<ins>大典太光世</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZRbHOynuosE?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZRbHOynuosE%3Flist%3DPLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9981898d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZRbHOynuosE?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8</a><br />\n自動導航auto神<br />\n<br />\n<ins>鬼丸國綱</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QA3lg5_5vUY?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQA3lg5_5vUY%3Flist%3DPLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=a185a908\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QA3lg5_5vUY?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8</a><br />\n超高爆發力 不過解S唔好用<br />\n<br />\n<ins>童子切安綱</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KH1yCcrJlxs?list=PLg4LQ522YIS1hHFM8dHoNhbrjy3FUyBs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKH1yCcrJlxs%3Flist%3DPLg