531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"有用資料<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑色狐狸面具抽到唔好突!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n巫劍名物帳<br />\n<a href=\"https://tenkahyakken.jp/character/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenkahyakken.jp%2Fcharacter%2F&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=2ad66c28\" target=\"_blank\">https://tenkahyakken.jp/character/</a><br />\n<br />\n公式twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tenka_zan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftenka_zan&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e95b3fa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tenka_zan</a><br />\n<br />\n官方wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://tenka-zan-wiki.gamematome.jp/game/979/wiki/%E3%83%88%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%9A%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenka-zan-wiki.gamematome.jp%2Fgame%2F979%2Fwiki%2F%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2583%2583%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%259A%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2582%25B8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e2fd2e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tenka-zan-wiki.gamematome.jp/game/979/wiki/%E3%83%88%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%9A%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://天華百劍.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A4%A9%E8%8F%AF%E7%99%BE%E5%8A%8D.net&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7f5c9f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">天華百劍.net</a> wiki (有全角色評價 打名search)<br />\n<a href=\"http://xn--7drx8nww1ai4l.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxn--7drx8nww1ai4l.net%2F&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f0c0183f\" target=\"_blank\">http://xn--7drx8nww1ai4l.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ.新手初期應該點做?<br />\n<br />\n-刷完首抽就去關注高戰力大腿 用等級檢索 單方面follow就可以用<br />\n<br />\n-打活動升巫劍等級<br />\n<br />\n-做依頼升親愛度等級 解放裝備空格(lv10,20,45都會解放多1格)<br />\n<br />\n-工房可以強化技同刀裝 無課初期唔建議突抽既UR裝 活動裝同技全部可以突<br />\n<br />\n-突破巫劍上限 game刷返黎既銅錢可以抽sr角色同裝備<br />\n(抽到相同就會自動突破 突滿再抽到就會變成突破道具 可以用黎突其他角色)<br />\n<br />\n另外營運好佛 討伐活動送突破道具同定期有活動送skin<br />\n關卡打輸都無所謂 輸左唔會扣體 可以即管嘗試挑戰高難度任務<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">御三家超越條件:</span></ins><br />\n1. 等級80lv <br />\n2. 親密度50lv <br />\n3. 三頁全開花 <br />\n4. 打完主線第二章(初級都得) 之後會喺ミッション睇到超越任務同埋帶佢地落場打200場既進度<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n巫劍調教等級變化<br />\n20 表情轉變(微笑)、獲得贈禮時的語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n21 依賴後語音變化<br />\n23 設定愛刀後進入首頁的語音變化<br />\n26 磨刀語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n28 觸摸語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n35 表情轉變(臉紅)、依賴後及獲得贈禮時的語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n37 設定愛刀後進入首頁的語音變化<br />\n40 磨刀語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n42 觸摸語音變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n44 視姦語音變化(放大後凝望重點部位就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n識別語音圖鑑編號<br />\n1,2 遊戲場語音<br />\n3,4,5,6 開啟遊戲第一次進入首頁，由巫劍點入角色的打招呼(早&gt;白天&gt;晚&gt;深夜)<br />\n7 長時間放置不管臉紅語音<br />\n8 出太多任務、依賴/委託臉紅語音<br />\n9,10,11 設定愛刀後進入首頁(好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n12,13,14 設定愛刀後進入首頁(好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n15,16,17 設定愛刀後進入首頁(好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n18,19,20 觸摸語音(好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n21,22,23 觸摸語音2 (好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n24 未知(拒絕)<br />\n25,26,27 胸襲語音 (好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n28,29,30 胸襲語音2 (好感低&gt;中&gt;高)<br />\n31 未知(生氣)<br />\n32, 33遊戲閒置語音(推測是好&gt;高，只有兩段變化)<br />\n34 首次抽到語音<br />\n35,36 未知<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n其他有用小知識<br />\n-刀裝同巫劍同屬性會有1.5倍效果<br />\n-技能限界突破後會增加彈數<br />\n-出技會有無敵時間 可以用黎避招<br />\n-不停重複做依賴就會解放上級依賴<br />\n-劍巫鐘意邊一類既禮物 可以由能力開花裡面全開花bonus睇到 主要分4種<br />\n-任務要拎S就要全隊接近滿血過關(拾回復HP道具都無問題)<br />\n-雙倍exp boost每半個鐘回1格 隨便用"},{"pid":"0357e3d3d16bd211f23d6f2c35b42cad2a481afd","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">劍巫得意依賴 2倍親愛exp/道具選項<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM8PgqV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM8PgqV.jpg&h=bc89ae8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8X4PLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8X4PLV.jpg&h=02ff3807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPcgFSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPcgFSB.jpg&h=f77335a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3vh9LW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3vh9LW.jpg&h=b493f1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"6a4eac102e906082a2e673a6074761628ce46414","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"刷完首抽記得follow lv200大腿<br />\n<br />\n新玩無耐 戰力唔夠而又想打獄級協力 都可以留ID一齊玩<br />\n<br />\n最好著好血防裝同自己揾位匿埋生存到最後 <br />\n<br />\n共鬥要先互相follow 然後入場前將 &quot;相互follow以外受付&quot; 既box轉做藍色先入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1228d346faf4bad05e36457a25d49d4a5f76f68","tid":1138531,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e232140ff492bd5adbda5b36557d2d533e755552","tid":1138531,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"你等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji